            "answer_text": "There is nothing incorrect about either of those phrases, but \u201cMay I know?\u201d is awkward. Nobody says that. \u201cJust wanted to ask\u201d is what you\u2019re looking for. You could also try, \u201cHey, quick question,\u201d or, \u201cCan I ask you something?\u201d ",
